text: Saint-Agnan, Aisne is a former commune. It is found in the region Hauts-de- France in the Aisne department in the north of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Vallées-en-Champagne.Arrêté préfectoral 23 November 2015 ==References== Category:Former communes in Aisne
title: Saint-Agnan, Aisne
